  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IN A NUTSHELL</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to pick up. All you need is the mouse or a single stick with two buttons.<br></li><li>Daily mini-campaign. Each day missions are a bit different than the last.<br></li><li>Endless mode. See how far you can go.<br></li><li>Simple aircraft setup. 27 possible combinations to accomodate your play style.<br></li><li>Arcade action. Score as much as you can, compete on the leaderboards.<br></li><li>Quick to get into action. No deep story or cutscenes to suffer through, just dogfights.<br></li><li>Quick installation. Minimum requirements but vibrant visuals.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608120/extras/0e7ad02ebc956e9e3c22da281cc4a67c.poster.avif?t=1684481176\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608120/extras/0e7ad02ebc956e9e3c22da281cc4a67c.webm?t=1684481176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608120/extras/0e7ad02ebc956e9e3c22da281cc4a67c.mp4?t=1684481176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
